{"discussions":[{"id":"d1","authorId":"u1","authorName":"李同学","authorRole":"student","title":"质壁分离为什么用0.3g/mL的蔗糖溶液？","content":"做质壁分离实验时老师强调要用0.3g/mL蔗糖溶液，浓度太高或太低会怎样？","createTime":1782554400000,"chapterId":"ch4","replies":[{"id":"r1","authorId":"u2","authorName":"王老师","authorRole":"teacher","content":"好问题！0.3g/mL蔗糖溶液浓度适中，能引起质壁分离但不会导致细胞死亡，换成清水后可以复原。如果浓度过高（如0.5g/mL以上），细胞失水过度会死亡，无法复原；浓度过低则不会发生明显的质壁分离。","createTime":1782640800000}]},{"id":"d2","authorId":"u2","authorName":"王老师","authorRole":"teacher","title":"光合作用光反应与暗反应的联系（重点）","content":"光反应为暗反应提供什么？暗反应为光反应提供什么？请同学们思考并回复。","createTime":1782468000000,"chapterId":"ch5","replies":[{"id":"r2","authorId":"u1","authorName":"李同学","authorRole":"student","content":"光反应为暗反应提供ATP和NADPH（[H]），暗反应为光反应提供ADP和NADP+。","createTime":1782554400000}]},{"id":"d_1782731474392_tf9d","authorId":"u4_1782567917951","authorName":"杨老师","authorRole":"student","title":"111","content":"11212","chapterId":"ch1","createTime":1782731474392,"replies":[{"id":"r_1782731480862_1k4m","authorId":"u4_1782567917951","authorName":"杨老师","authorRole":"student","content":"212","createTime":1782731480862},{"id":"r_1782731494759_7f6m","authorId":"u2","authorName":"王老师","authorRole":"teacher","content":"阿萨大大","createTime":1782731494759}]}],"updatedAt":"2026-06-29T11:11:35.639Z"}